    <p class="font-semibold mt-4">Calculator Connection:</p>
    <p>
      Input the number of dumpsters you currently own, along with your desired rental frequency. The tool will show you how optimizing your inventory can help you scale revenue without overspending on additional equipment.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-4">
      Clayton's insights are a reminder that running a successful dumpster rental business isn't just about having the right equipmentâ€”it's about strategy. By experimenting with the calculator's inputs, you can test ideas, refine your pricing, and plan for additional revenue streams.
